assuming roles 4 dummies

1. gitbash in c/Users/(your local user)
2. source mypython/Scripts/activate
3. cd C:/awsconnect-win-x64
4. ./awsconnect --role WH-00H1-role_READONLY
5. paste link into browser
6. export AWS_DEFAULT_PROFILE=WH-00H1-role_READONLY
7. for some reason that doesn't work, so copy the new role and paste over default
